### 2. Understand the specification domain

**Critical**: Before defining principles, understand what specification this specification defines:
- What domain does this specification serve? (APIs, Data Formats, Communication Specifications?)
- What entities are needed? (Server, Tool, Resource, Message?)
- What operations are defined? (CRUD, Events, RPC?)
